info.name: Maroon 5 Logo Button (Tumblr)
info.description: An add to the first Maroon 5's dashboard theme.Change the Tumblr Logo on the top left of your dashboard for the best band ever mark. It looks gorgeous! Enjoy.
info.additionalInfo:
Version 1.0
|Instruction:
 - Click the installing button.
|Important Info:
 - Make sure you have the needed plug-ins intalled on your browser.
 - Only for Google Chrome and Mozilla Firefox.
 - It's suggested that you use the Maroon 5 Dashboard Theme and Background as well.
